Package com.qaitsolutions.pframe.core.testng

Class PFrameListener

java.lang.Object
com.qaitsolutions.pframe.core.testng.PFrameListener
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.testng.IConfigurationListener, org.testng.ISuiteListener, org.testng.ITestListener, org.testng.ITestNGListener
public class PFrameListener extends Object implements org.testng.ISuiteListener, org.testng.ITestListener, org.testng.IConfigurationListener
TestNg implementation of listener that will be used to configure the test execution and reporting. This links testNg, extent report and log4j.

Since:
1.0
Author:
Iulian Andrei (iulian.andrei@qaitsolutions.com)
